quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  18,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  18,1,tareef Allah ke liye hai jis ne apne bande par yeh kitaab nazil ki aur is mein koi theerh nah rakhi
  18,2,"theek theek seedhi baat kehnay wali kitaab, taakay woh logon ko khuda ke sakht azaab se khabardaar kar day, aur imaan laa kar naik amal karne walon ko khushkhabri deeday ke un ke liye acha ajar hai"
  18,3,jis mein woh hamesha rahen ge
  18,4,aur unn logon ko dara day jo kehte hain ke Allah ne kisi ko beta banaya hai
  18,5,iss baat ka nah unhen koi ilm hai aur nah un ke baap dada ko tha barri baat hai jo un ke mun se nikalti hai woh mehez jhoot bektay hain
  18,6,"acha, to ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, shayad tum un ke peechay gham ke maaray apni jaan kho dainay walay ho agar yeh iss taleem par imaan nah laaye"
  18,7,waqea yeh hai ke yeh jo kuch sir o samaan bhi zameen par hai is ko hum ne zameen ki zeenat banaya hai taakay inn logon ko aazmayin inn mein kon behtar amal karne wala hai
  18,8,aakhir kaar iss sab ko hum aik chtil maidan bana dainay walay hain
  18,9,kya tum samajte ho ke ghaar aur kunbay walay hamari koi barri ajeeb nshanyon mein se thay ?
  18,10,"jab woh chand nojawan ghaar mein panah gzin hue aur unhon ne kaha ke"" ae parvar-digaar, hum ko apni rehmat khaas se Nawaz aur hamara maamla durust kar day, """
  18,11,to hum ne inhen usi ghaar mein thpk kar salha saal ke liye gehri neend sulaa diya
  18,12,phir hum ne inhen uthaya taakay dekhen unn ke do garohoon mein se kon apni muddat qiyam ka theek shumaar karta hai
  18,13,hum un ka asal qissa tumhe sunaate hain woh chand nojawan thay jo apne rab par imaan le aeye thay aur hum ne un ko hadaayat mein taraqqi bakhsh thi
  18,14,"hum ne un ke dil uss waqt mazboot kar diye jab woh utthay aur unhon ne elaan kar diya ke"" hamara rab to bas wohi hai jo asmano aur zameen ka rab hai hum ussay chore kar kisi dosray mabood ko nah pukaarain ge agar hum aisa karen to bilkul beja baat karen ge """
  18,15,"( phir unhon ne aapas mein aik dosray se kaha )"" yeh hamari qoum to Rab kaayenaat ko chore kar dosray khuda bana baithi hai yeh log un ke mabood honay par koi wazeh Daleel kyun nahi laatay? aakhir uss shakhs se bara zalim aur kon ho sakta hai jo Allah par jhoot bandhay ?"
  18,16,"ab jabkay tum un se aur inn ke معبودان ghair Allah se be talluq ho chuke ho to chalo ab falan ghaar mein chal kar panah lau tumhara rab tum par apni rehmat ka daman wasee kere ga aur tumahray kaam ke liye sir o samaan muhayya kar day ga """
  18,17,tum inhen ghaar mein dekhte to tumhe yun nazar aata ke Sooraj jab nikalta hai to un ke ghaar ko chore kar dayen janib charh jata hai aur jab ghuroob hota hai to un se bach kar baen janib utar jata hai aur woh hain ke ghaar ke andar aik wasee jagah mein parre hain yeh Allah ki nshanyon mein se aik hai jis ko Allah hadaayat day wohi hadaayat panay wala hai aur jisay Allah bhatka day is ke liye tum koi walii murshid nahi pa satke
  18,18,"tum inhen dekh kar yeh samajte ke woh jaag rahay hain, halaank woh so rahay thay hum inhen dayen baen karvat dlwate rehtay thay aur un ka kutta ghaar ke dhanay par haath phelaaye betha tha agar tum kahin jhaank kar unhen dekhte to ultay paon bhaag kharray hotay aur tum par un ke nazare se dehshat baith jati"
  18,19,"aur isi ajeeb karishmay se hum ne inhen utha bithaya taakay zara aapas mein pooch gach karen un mein se aik ne poocha"" kaho kitni der is haal mein rahay ?"" dosaron ne kaha"" shayad din bhar ya is se kuch kam rahay hon ge"" phir woh bolay"" Allah hi behtar jaanta hai ke hamara kitna waqt is haalat mein guzra chalo, ab apne mein se kisi ko chandi ka yeh sikka day kar shehar bhejen aur woh dekhe ke sab se acha khana kahan milta hai wahan se woh kuch khanay ke liye laaye aur chahiye ke zara hoshyari se kaam kere, aisa nah ho ke woh kisi ko hamaray yahan honay se khabardaar kar baithy"
  18,20,"agar kahin unn logon ka haath hum par par gaya to bas sangsar hi kar dalain ge, ya phir zabardasti hamein apni millat mein wapas le jayen ge, aur aisa howa tawaham kabhi Falah nah pa saken ge """
  18,21,"iss terhan hum ne ahal shehar ko un ke haal par mutala kya taakay log jaan len ke Allah ka wada sacha hai aur yeh ke qayamat ki gharri be shak aa kar rahay gi ( magar zara khayaal karo ke jab sochnay ki asal baat yeh thi ) uss waqt woh aapas mein iss baat par jhagar rahay thay ke inn ( ashaab kahaf ) ke sath kya kya jaye kuch logon ne kaha"" inn par aik deewar chunn do, un ka rab hi inn ke maamla ko behtar jaanta hai"" magar jo log unn ke mamlaat par ghalib thay unhon ne kaha"" hum to un par aik ibadat gaah banayen ge """
  18,22,"kuch log kahin ge ke woh teen thay aur choutha un ka kutta tha aur kuch dosray keh den ge ke paanch thay aur chhata unn ka kutta tha yeh sab bay-tuki hanktayhain kuch aur log kehte hain ke saat thay aur aathwan unn ka kutta tha kaho, mera rab hi behtar jaanta hai ke woh kitney thay kam hi log un ki sahih tadaad jantay hain pas tum sarsari baat se barh kar un ki tadaad ke muamlay mein logon se behas nah karo, aur nah un ke mutaliq kisi se kuch pucho"
  18,23,"aur dekho, kisi cheez ke baray mein kabhi yeh nah kaha karo ke mein kal yeh kaam kar dun ga"
  18,24,"( tum kuch nahi kar satke ) ila yeh ke Allah chahay agar bhoolay se aisi baat zabaan se nikal jaye to foran apne rab ko yaad karo aur kaho"" umeed hai ke mera rab iss muamlay mein Rashd se qareeb tar baat ki taraf meri rahnumai farma day ga """
  18,25,"aur woh apne ghaar mein teen so saal rahay, aur ( kuch log mddt ke shumaar mein )? saal aur barh gay hain"
  18,26,"tum kaho, Allah un ke qiyam ki mddt ziyada jaanta hai, asmano aur zameen ke sab posheeda ahwaal usi ko maloom hain, kya khoob hai woh dekhnay wala aur suneney wala! zameen o aasman ki makhloqaat ka koi khabr geer uss ke siwa nahi, aur woh apni hukoomat mein kisi ko shareek nahi karta"
  18,27,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! tumahray rab ki kitaab mein se jo kuch tum par wahi kya gaya hai usay ( jon ka ton ) suna do, koi uss ke frmodat ko badal dainay ka majaz nahi hai, ( aur agar tum kisi ki khatir is mein radd o badal karo ge to ) uss se bach kar bhagnay ke liye koi jaye panah nah pao ge"
  18,28,"aur apne dil ko unn logon ki mayt par mutmaen karo jo apne rab ki Raza ke talab gaar ban kar subah o shaam ussay pkarte hain, aur unn se hargiz nigah nah phero kya tum duniya ki zeenat pasand karte ho? kisi aisay shakhs ki itaat nah karo jis ke dil ko hum ne apni yaad se ghaafil kar diya hai aur jis ne apni khwahish nafs ki pairwi ikhtiyar kar li hai aur jis ka tareeq car afraat o tafreet par mabni hai"
  18,29,"saaf keh do ke yeh haq hai tumahray rab ki taraf se, ab jis ka jee chahay maan le aur jis ka jee chahay inkaar kar day hum ne ( inkaar karne walay ) zaalmon ke liye aik aag tayyar kar rakhi hai jis ki laptayninhen ghairay mein le chuki hain wahan agar woh pani mangain ge tu aisay pani se un ki tawaza ki jaye gi jo tail ki tilchat jaissa hoga aur un ka mun bhon daaley ga, bad tareen peenay ki cheez aur bohat buri Aaraamgah !"
  18,30,"rahay woh log jo maan len aur naik amal karen, to yaqeenan hum naiko car logon ka ajar zaya nahi kya karte"
  18,31,"un ke liye sada bahhar jannaten hain jin ke neechay nhrin beh rahi hon gi, wahan woh sonay ke kanganon se aaraasta kiye jayen ge, bareek resham aur Atlas o Deeba ke sabz kapray pehnein ge, aur onchi masnadonpar takiye laga kar bathain ge behtareen ajar aur aala darjay ki jaye qiyam !"
  18,32,ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! inn ke samnay aik misaal paish karo do shakhs thay un mein se aik ko hum ne angoor ke do baagh diye aur unn ke gird khajoor ke darakhton ki barh lagai aur un ke darmain kaasht ki zameen rakhi
  18,33,dono baagh khoob phalay phoolay aur baar aawar honay mein unhon ne zara si kasar bhi nah choari unn baghoon ke andar hum ne aik neher jari kar di
  18,34,"aur se khoob naffa haasil howa yeh kuch pa kar aik din woh apne hamsaye se baat karte hue bola"" mein tujh se ziyada maldaar hon aur tujh se ziyada taaqatwar nafri rakhta hon """
  18,35,"phir woh apni jannat mein daakhil howa aur apne nafs ke haq mein zalim ban kar kehnay laga"" mein nahi samjhta ke yeh doulat kabhi fanaa ho jaye gi"
  18,36,"aur mujhe tawaqqa nahi ke qayamat ki gharri kabhi aeye gi taham agar kabhi mujhe apne rab ke huzoor پلٹایا bhi gaya to zaroor iss se bhi ziyada shandaar jagah paon ga """
  18,37,"uss ke hamsaye ne guftagu karte hue is se kaha"" kya to kufar karta hai uss zaat se jis ne tujhe matti se aur phir nutfay se peda kya aur tujhe aik poora aadmi bana khara kya ?"
  18,38,"raha mein, to mera rab to wohi Allah hai aur mein is ke sath kisi ko shareek nahi karta"
  18,39,"aur jab to apni jannat mein daakhil ho raha tha to is waqt teri zabaan se yeh kyun nah nikla ke masha Allah , laa qoة ila ballh? agar to mujhe maal aur aulaad mein apne se kamtar pa raha hai"
  18,40,to baeed nahi ke mera rab mujhe teri jannat se behtar ataa farma day aur teri jannat par aasman se koi aafat bhaij day jis se woh saaf maidan ban kar reh jaye
  18,41,"ya is ka pani zameen mein utar jaye aur phir to usay kisi terhan nah nikaal sakay """
  18,42,"aakhir kaar howa yeh ke is ka sara Samrah mara gaya aur woh apne angarro ke baagh ko tattyun( chappar) par ulta para dekh kar apni lagai hui laagat par haath milta reh gaya aur kehnay laga ke"" kash! mein ne apne rab ke sath kisi ko shareek nahTehraya hota """
  18,43,"nah howa Allah ko chore kar is ke paas koi jatha ke is ki madad karta, aur nah kar saka woh aap hi is aafat ka muqaabla"
  18,44,"uss waqt maloom howa ke karsazi ka ikhtiyar khuday-e brhq hi ke liye hai, inaam wohi behtar hai jo woh bakhshay aur injaam wohi bakhair hai jo woh dukhaay"
  18,45,"aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! aِnhin hayaat duniya ki haqeeqat iss misaal se samjhao ke aaj hum ne aasman se pani barsa diya to zameen ki pod khob ghani ho gayi, aur kal wohi nabataat bhus ban kar reh gayi jisay hawae udaaye liye phurti hain Allah har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  18,46,yeh maal aur yeh aulaad mehez dunewi zindagi ki aik hungami Araish hai asal mein to baqi reh jaane wali naikian hi tairay rab ke nazdeek nateejay ke lehaaz se behtar hain aur aُnhi se achiumeedain wabsta ki ja sakti hain
  18,47,"fikar uss din ki honi chahiye jab ke hum pahoron ko chalayein ge, aur tum zameen ko bilkul burhenapa pao ge, aur hum tamam insanon ko is terhan ghair kar jama karen ge ke ( uglo pichlon mein se ) aik bhi nah chhootey ga"
  18,48,"aur sab ke sab tumahray rab ke huzoor saf Dur saf paish kiye jayen ge lau dekh lau, aa gay na tum hamaray paas usi terhan jaissa hum ne tum ko pehli baar peda kya tha tum ne to yeh samgha tha ke hum ne tumahray liye koi waday ka waqt muqarrar hi nahi kya hai"
  18,49,"aur nama aamaal samnay rakh diya jaye ga is waqt tum dekho ge ke mujrim log apni kitaab zindagi ke andrajaat se dar rahay hon ge aur keh rahay hon ge ke haae hamari kam bakhti, yeh kaisi kitaab hai ke hamari koi choti barri harkat aisi nahi rahi jo is mein darj nah ho gayi ho jo jo kuch unhon ne kya tha woh sab apne samnay haazir payen ge aur tera rab kisi par zara zulm nah kere ga"
  18,50,"yaad karo, jab hum ne firshton se kaha ke aadam ko sajda karo to unhon ne sajda kya magar iblees ne nah kya woh junoo mein se tha is liye apne rab ke hukum ki itaat se nikal gaya ab kya tum mujhe chore kar uss ko aur is ki zaryat ko apna sarparast banatay ho halaank woh tumahray dushman hain? bara hi bura badal hai jisay zalim log ikhtiyar kar rahay hain"
  18,51,mein ne aasman o zameen peda karte waqt unn ko nahi bulaya tha aur nah khud unn ki apni takhleeq mein inhen shareek kya tha mera yeh kaam nahi hai ke gumraah karne walon ko apna madad gaar banaya karoon
  18,52,"phir kya karen ge yeh log uss roz jabkay inn ka rab inn se kahe ga ke poukaro ab unn hstyon ko jinhein tum mera shareek samajh baithy thay yeh un ko pukaarain ge, magar woh inn ki madad ko nah ayen ge aur hum un ke darmain aik hi halakat ka garha mushtarik kar den ge"
  18,53,saaray mujrim uss roz aag dekhen ge اaur samajhlain ge ke ab inhen is mein girna hai aur woh is se bachney ke liye koi jaye panah nah payen ge
  18,54,hum ne iss quran mein logon ko terhan terhan se samjhaya magar ensaan bara hi jhagralu waqay howa hai
  18,55,"unn ke samnay jab hadaayat aayi to usay maan-ne aur apne rab ke huzoor maffi chahanay se aakhir unn koks cheez ne rok diya? iss ke siwa aur kuch nahi ke woh muntazir hain ke unn ke sath bhi wohi kuch ho jo pichli qomon ke sath ho chuka hai, ya yeh ke woh azaab ko samnay atay dekh len !"
  18,56,Rasolo-n ko hum is kaam ke siwa aur kisi gharz ke liye nahi bhaijtay ke woh basharat aur tanbeeh ki khidmat injaam day den magar kafiroon ka haal yeh hai ke woh baatil ke hathyaar le kar haq ko neecha dikhaane ki koshish karte hain aur unhon ne meri ayaat ko aur unn tnbihat ko jo inhen ki gayeen mazaq bana liya hai
  18,57,"aur uss shakhs se barh kar zalim aur kon hai jisay is ke rab ki ayaat suna kar nasiyaat ki jaye aur woh unn se mun phairay aur uss buray injaam ko bhool jaye jis ka sir o samaan is ne apne liye khud apne hathon kya hai? ( jin logon ne yeh rawish ikhtiyar ki hai ) un ke dilon par hum ne ghilaaf charha diye hain jo inhen quran ki baat nahi samajhney dete, aur unn ke kaanon mein hum ne gharani peda kar di hai tum inhen hadaayat ki taraf kitna hi bulaao, woh is haalat mein kabhi hadaayat nah payen ge"
  18,58,tera rab bara dar guzar karne wala aur Raheem hai woh un ke krtoton par inhen pakarna chahta to jaldi hi azaab bhaij deta magar un ke liye waday ka aik waqt muqarrar hai aur is se bach kar bhaag niklny ki yeh koi raah nah payen ge
  18,59,"yeh azaab Raseedah bastiyan tumahray samnay mojood hain unhon ne jab zulm kya to hum ne inhen halaak kar diya, aur un mein se har aik ki halakat ke liye hum ne waqt muqarrar kar rakha tha"
  18,60,"( zara inn ko woh qissa sunaaoo jo moose ko paish aaya tha ) jabkay moose ne apne khadim se kaha tha ke"" mein apna safar khatam nah karoon ga jab taq ke dono daryaaon ke sngm par nah poanch jaoon, warna mein aik zamana daraaz taq chalta hi rahon ga """
  18,61,pas jab woh un ke sngm par puhanche to apni machhli se ghaafil ho gay aur woh nikal kar is terhan darya mein chali gayi jaisay ke koi surang lagi ho
  18,62,"agay ja kar moose ne apne khadim se kaha"" lao hamara nashta, aaj ke safar mein to hum buri terhan thak gay hain """
  18,63,"khadim ne kaha"" aap ne dekha! yeh kya howa? jab hum uss chattaan ke paas thire hue thay uss waqt mujhe machhli ka khayaal nah raha aur shetan ne mujh ko aisa ghaafil kar diya ke mein is ka zikar ( aap se karna ) bhool gaya machhli to ajeeb tareeqay se nikal kar darya mein chali gayi """
  18,64,"moose ne kaha"" isi ki to hamein talaash thi"" chunancha woh dono apne naqsh qadam par phir wapas hue"
  18,65,aur wahan unhon ne hamaray bundon mein se aik bande ko paaya jisay hum ne apni rehmat se nawaza tha aur apni taraf se aik khaas ilm ataa kya tha
  18,66,"moose ne is se kaha"" kya mein aap ke sath reh sakta hon taakay aap mujhe bhi uss Danish ki taleem den jo aap ko sikhaigayi hai? """
  18,67,"is ne jawab diya"" aap mere sath sabr nahi kar satke"
  18,68,"aur jis cheez ki aap ko khabar nah ho aakhir aap is par sabr kar bhi kaisay satke hain """
  18,69,"moose ne kaha"" Insha Allah aap mujhe sabir payen ge aur mein kisi maamla mein aap ki nafarmani nah karoon ga """
  18,70,"is ne kaha"" acha, agar aap mere sath chaltay hain to mujh se koi baat nah poucheen jab taq ke mein khud is ka aap se zikar nah karoon """
  18,71,"ab woh dono rawana hue, yahan taq ke jab woh aik kashti mein sawaar ho gay to is shakhs ne kashti mein shagaaf daal diya moose ne kaha"" aap ne is mein shagaaf daal diya taakay sab kashti walon ko duubo den? yeh to aap ne aik sakht harkat kar daali """
  18,72,"is ne kaha"" mein ne tum se kaha nah tha ke tum mere sath sabr nahi kar satke? """
  18,73,"moose ne kaha"" bhool chowk par mujhe nah pakriyay mere muamlay mein aap zara sakhti se kaam nah len """
  18,74,"phir woh dono chalay, yahan taq ke un ko aik larka mila aur is shakhs ne usay qatal kar diya moose ne kaha"" aap ne aik be gunah ki jaan le li halaank uss ne kisi ka khoon nah kya tha? yeh kaam to aap ne bohat hi bura kya """
  18,75,"uss ne kaha"" mein ne tum se kaha nah tha ke tum mere sath sabr nahi kar satke? """
  18,76,"moose ne kaha"" is ke baad agar mein aap se kuch pouchon to aap mujhe sath nah rakhen lijiye, ab to meri taraf se aap ko izr mil gaya """
  18,77,"phir woh agay chalay yahan taq ke aik bastii mein puhanche aur wahan ke logon se khana manga magar unhon ne un dono ki ziyafat se inkaar kar diya wahan unhon ne aik deewar dekhi jo gira chahti thi uss shakhs ne is deewar ko phir qaim kar diya moose ne kaha"" agar aap chahtay to is kaam ki aُjrt le satke thay """
  18,78,"uss ne kaha"" bas mera tumhara sath khatam howa ab mein tumhe un baton ki haqeeqat batata hon jin par tum sabr nah kar sakay"
  18,79,"uss kashti ka maamla yeh hai ke woh chand ghareeb admion ki thi jo darya mein mehnat mazdoori karte thay mein ne chaha ke usay aib daar kar dun, kyunkay agay aik aisay badshah ka ilaqa tha jo har kashti ko zabardasti chean laita tha"
  18,80,"raha woh larka, to is ke walidain momin thay, hamein andesha howa ke yeh larka apni sar kashi aur kufar se un ko tang kere ga"
  18,81,is liye hum ne chaha ke un ka rab is ke badlay un ko aisi aulaad day jo ikhlaq mein bhi is se behtar ho aur jis se sila rehmi bhi ziyada mutawaqqa ho
  18,82,"aur is deewar ka maamla yeh hai ke yeh do yateem larkoon ki hai jo is shehar mein rehtay hain is deewar ke neechay inn bchchon ke liye aik khazana madfoon hai aur un ka baap aik naik aadmi tha is liye tumahray rab ne chaha ke yeh dono bachay baaligh hon aur apna khazana nikaal len yeh tumahray rab ki rehmat ki bana parkia gaya hai, mein ne kuch apne ikhtiyar se nahi kar diya hai yeh hai haqeeqat unn baton ki jin par tum sabr nah kar sakay """
  18,83,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yeh log tum se zwalqrnin ke baray mein puchhte hain un se kaho, mein is ka kuch haal tum ko sunataa hon"
  18,84,hum ne is ko zameen mein Iqtidaar ataa kar rakha tha aur usay har qisam ke asbaab o wasail bakhshay thay
  18,85,is ne ( pehlay maghrib ki taraf aik muhim ka ) sir o samaan kya
  18,86,"hatta ke jab woh ghuroob aftaab ki had taq poanch gaya to is ne Sooraj ko aik kalay pani mein doubtey dekha aur wahan ussay aik qoum mili hum ne kaha"" ae zwalqrnin, tujhe yeh mqdrt bhi haasil hai ke un ko takleef pohnnchaye aur yeh bhi ke inn ke sath naik royih ikhtiyar kere """
  18,87,"is ne kaha,"" jo un mein se zulm kere ga hum is ko saza den ge, phir woh apne rab ki taraf pultaya jaye ga aur woh usay aur ziyada sakht azaab day ga"
  18,88,"aur jo un mein se imaan laaye ga aur naik amal kere ga uss ke liye achi jaza hai aur hum is ko naram ehkaam den ge """
  18,89,phir uss ne ( aik doosri muhim ki ) tayari ki
  18,90,yahan taq ke Tulu aftaab ki hadd taq ja pouncha wahan is ne dekha ke Sooraj aik aisi qoum par tulu ho raha hai jis ke liye dhoop se bachney ka koi samaan hum ne nahi kya hai
  18,91,"yeh haal tha unn ka, aur zwalqrnin ke paas jo kuch tha ussay hum jantay thay"
  18,92,phir is ne ( aik aur muhim ka ) samaan kya
  18,93,yahan taq ke jab do pahoron ke darmain pouncha to usay un ke paas aik qoum mili jo mushkil hi se koi baat samjhti thi
  18,94,"unn logon ne kaha ke"" ae zwalqrnin, yajooj aur majooj is sarzamen mein fasaad pheilatay hain to kya hum tujhe koi tax is kaam ke liye den ke to hamaray aur un ke darmain aik band taamer kar day? """
  18,95,"is ne kaha"" jo kuch mere rab ne mujhe day rakha hai woh bohat hai tum bas mehnat se meri madad karo, mein tumahray aur un ke darmain band banaye deta hon"
  18,96,"mujhe lohay ki chadrin laa kar do"" aakhir jab dono pahoron ke darmiyani khalaa ko is ne paat diya to logon se kaha ke ab aag dehka-o hatta ke jab ( yeh aahinii deewar ) bilkul aag ki terhan surKh ho gayi to is ne kaha"" lao, ab mein is par pighla howa tanba اundaylon ga """
  18,97,( yeh band aisa tha ke ) yajooj o majooj is par charh kar bhi nah aa satke thay aur is mein naqb lagana un ke liye aur bhi mushkil tha
  18,98,"zwalqrnin ne kaha"" yeh mere rab ki rehmat hai magar jab mere rab ke waday ka waqt aayega to woh is ko pewand khaak kar day ga, aur mere rab ka wada brhq hai """
  18,99,aur uss roz hum logon ko chore den ge ke ( samandar ki moajoon ki terhan ) aik doosray se ghutham ghutha hon aur soor phuuNkaa jaye ga aur hum sab insanon ko aik sath jama karen ge
  18,100,aur woh din hoga jab hum jahannum ko kafiroon ke samnay layein ge
  18,101,unn kafiroon ke samnay jo meri nasiyaat ki taraf se andhay banay hue thay aur kuch suneney ke liye tayyar hi nah thay
  18,102,"to kya yeh log, jinhon ne kufar ikhtiyar kya hai, yeh khayaal rakhtay hain ke mujhe chore kar mere bundon ko apna karsaaz bana len? hum ne aisay kafiroon ki ziyafat ke liye jahannum tayyar kar rakhi hai"
  18,103,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho, kya hum tumhe bitayen ke apne aamaal mein sab se ziyada nakaam o namuraad log kon hain ?"
  18,104,woh ke duniya ki zindagi mein jin ki saari sae o jehed raah e raast se bhatki rahi aur woh samajte rahay ke woh sab kuch theek kar rahay hain
  18,105,"yeh woh log hain jinhon ne apne rab ki ayaat ko maan-ne se inkaar kya aur is ke huzoor paishi ka yaqeen nah kya is liye unn ke saaray aamaal zaya ho gay, qayamat ke roz hum inhen koi wazan nah den ge"
  18,106,un ki jaza jahannum hai uss kufar ke badlay jo unhon ne kya aur uss mazaq ki Padaash mein jo woh meri ayaat aur mere Rasolo-n ke sath karte rahay
  18,107,"albtt_h woh log jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye, un ki maizbani ke liye Firdous ke baagh hon ge"
  18,108,jin mein woh hamesha rahen ge aur kabhi uss jagah se nikal kar kahin jaane ko unn ka jee nah chahay ga
  18,109,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kaho ke agar samandar mere rab ki baatein likhnay ke liye roshnaye ban jaye to woh khatam ho jaye magar mere rab ki baatein khatam nah hon, balkay itni hi roshnaye hum aur le ayen to woh bhi kifayat nah kere"
  18,110,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kaho ke mein to aik ensaan hon tum hi jaissa, meri taraf wahi ki jati hai ke tumhara khuda bas aik hi khuda hai, pas jo koi apne rab ki mulaqaat ka umeed waar ho usay chahiye ke naik amal kere aur bandagi mein apne rab ke sath kisi aur ko shareek nah kere"
